      • getJSInstanceSpecifications

        public static Map<String,JavaScriptFactories.InstanceSpecification> getJSInstanceSpecifications(String packageName)
        Get this list of all JavaScript specifications within the given package. This is the base names of all javascript files (ending with .js or .jsyt) found in the given package.
        Parameters:
        packageName - the name of the package in which to search for specifications.
        Returns:
        never null. Basenames of javascript resources files in the same package as this class anywhere on the classpath.
